<html>
<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
bandage [victim] :<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
This skill allows you to bandage the wounds of someone who is mortally<br>
wounded so that they do not die.  It requires the possession of a bandage<br>
or tourniquet.  These can be bought at most provision shops.<br>
</html>
</body>
